{"tid":2159262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法援署署長鄺寶昌阻止警暴受害者告香港警魔證明歸英係好重要","createTime":"2020-08-16T08:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T16:29:00.000Z","uid":26770,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7e1ef50713901ca9f4aa67f3f9094a6f932814","tid":2159262,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2110769/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2110769/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1)刑事檢控專員老仆街梁卓然<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1827880/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1827880/page/1</a><br />\n由的士司機鄭國泉故意撞人案看刑事檢控專員梁卓然的本質<br />\n梁卓然涉誣告街坊以恐嚇遭警察輪姦的受害人不敢指證暴行<br />\n<br />\n2)監警會主席林鄭奴才梁定邦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2025287/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2025287/page/1</a><br />\n[踢爆梁定邦]無辜被打理論的真正演繹及監警會支持強姦示威者<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>點解又loop一次,<span class=\"xx-large\">睇到法援署署長鄺寶昌迫害受害人</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">證明香港所有握有公權力的法律界位已經全面滲透</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一定要借助獨立國家的情報資源先捉內鬼,唔係一人人票後呢班人都會暗中攪局"},{"pid":"b42b33ec4f715429ba78cfdb7acc84c8f0d68986","tid":2159262,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7054c5faedba6920a840b8a0624cf9f7a1871d9","tid":2159262,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42b33ec4f715429ba78cfdb7acc84c8f0d68986","tid":2159262,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n香港警魔非法公開示威者資料<br />\n因為部分示威者人係剛剛結婚搬走,連銀行信address都未改<br />\n係得香港警魔手上有<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">私隱專員黃雞兒條19律師從來無出聲</span>"},{"pid":"ee61db6038c41576bc7fd1729672f1a43615043c","tid":2159262,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09: